        <h3>HTML</h3>
         <p>HTML stands for HyperText Markup Language.
            HTML is the building block of a webpage</p>
            <p>HTML consist of elements known as Tags.
            HTML is not case sensitive</p>
            <p>HTML Starts With &lt;html&gt;Tag
            HTML Ends With &lt;/html&gt; Tag</p>
            <div class="bg-success">
            <h4> Basic Syntax of HTML</h4>
            <p>&lt;html&gt;</p>
            <p>&lt;head&gt;</p>
            <p>&lt;title&gt;
            &lt;/title&gt;</p>
            <p>&lt;/head&gt;</p>
            <p>&lt;body&gt;
            &lt;/body&gt;</p>
            <p>&lt;/html&gt;</p>
            </div>
